Compiling:

Import project using intelliJ.
Use gradle and kotlin.

Running:


Files overview: -

Use InputRunner.kt this is the entry point.

The main class for the Genetic Algorithm is GA.kt

Individual.kt has things relating to an individual, and crossover and mutation operators

TextAnalysis.kt has code for the fitness function.

The provided java code for encryption, decryption and fitness using monograms is inside Vigenere.java

